	{"x4pointer":" "
	 ,"x4code":null
	,"x4freetext":["The correction factor, which converts the flux measured"
		,"by the BC-501A detector to the flux in the gamma-ray"
		,"measurement with water is 1.09."
		,"Neutron flux 1.87 X 10**10 /Sr/uC, post-correction."]
	}
